Organization Rules
==================

Ruby Files (.rb)
  • Core logic → /lib/*.rb
  • Tests → /spec/*_spec.rb  
  • Integration scripts → /scripts/*.rb

Python Files (.py)
  • Modules (importable) → /python/*.py
  • Integration (called by Ruby) → /scripts/*.py

Notebooks (.ipynb)
  • All notebooks → /python/notebooks/

Documentation (.md)
  • User guides → /docs/guides/
  • Technical docs → /docs/
  • Root only: README, STRUCTURE, TODO, KNOWN_ISSUES

Quick Commands
==============

Ruby CLI:
  ruby cli.rb clean data.csv
  ruby cli.rb add-features data.csv
  ruby cli.rb train-stacked-ensemble predictions/ actuals.csv

Python Direct:
  python -c "from python.advanced_features import AdvancedFeatures"
  jupyter notebook python/notebooks/

Tests:
  bundle exec rspec
  ruby -Ilib -Ispec spec/csv_cleaner_spec.rb
